Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:08.86,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}空に向けて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:11.30,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}まだ見えない
